			LOCAL = (RAND:5 + 1)
			IF LOCAL == 5
				PRINTFORM 十指交缠着
			ELSEIF LOCAL == 4
				PRINTFORM 并肩而坐
			ELSEIF LOCAL == 3
				PRINTFORM 稍微害羞着
			ELSEIF LOCAL == 2
				PRINTFORM 嬉闹玩耍着
			ELSEIF LOCAL == 1
				PRINTFORM 交换着微笑
